- extends "base.html"

- block title
  Account activated

- block content
  %h1 Account activated.
  - load humanize
  - if user
    %p Thanks for signing up! Now you can
      %a{'href':"/accounts/login/"} log in
  - else
    %p Sorry, it didn't work. Either your activation link was incorrect, or the activation key for your account has expired; activation keys are only valid for {{ expiration_days|apnumber }} days after registration.